{"id":247674,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-各地访民在京聚会反腐-抗议维稳打压（图/","date":"2012-08-18T06:01:36Z","modified":"2012-08-18T06:01:36Z","title":"维权网 | 各地访民在京聚会反腐  抗议维稳打压（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员冯卫民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日晚</span><span>，到北京上访的上海名医焦东海与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>多名各地在京访民聚集一堂，共议国事。访民们一致认为党和国家要长治久安，必须下决心铲除腐败滋生的环境，并声援焦医生坚持反腐败的义举。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>地方上现在腐败发展得十分严重，触目惊心，造成大批访民进京告状，腐败泛滥，国已不国。但地方当局出于维稳的目的，阻止公民依法上访，不让访民检举官员贪腐，致使贪官们逍遥法外，举报公民遭到严酷的打击报复，作为老党员的焦东海医生对此感到痛心不已！焦医生说自己上访说轻点是爱国，说重点是在救国。焦医生为国家前途担忧，鞠躬尽瘁上访申诉，感动了在京的全国各地的许多访民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家从四面八方赶到焦医生在北京的暂住处，声援焦医生。席间，各地访民对《北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>大安保指挥部启动》的消息发表自己的看法和担忧，认为当局对访民一味进行维稳式打压无助于建设和谐社会。聚会在齐声高唱《团结就是力量》和《国际歌》中结束。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span><span>参加聚会的各地访民有：上海：毛恒凤、王扣玛、金月花、许国治；湖北：夏幼华、向金凤、汤素芳、邹桂兰、李玉琴、万少华、詹三桂、邱清华、许静静、孙小环、扬忠梅、彭汉怀；河北：田兰、王心灵；吉林：董奎红；辽宁：刘力；河南：聂丽娜及圆圆、李玉凤、王金兰、梁长荣；江苏：居小玲等共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>余人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PlZV8vgXQMg/UC8fUjAh3RI/AAAAAAAALdU/-ujvx5ywIzU/s1600/%E7%84%A6%E4%B8%9C%E6%B5%B7%E7%AC%AC1%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%9B%E5%86%9B%E5%90%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%BC%A0%E8%8D%A3%E6%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%B7%E6%AD%A3%E7%A5%A5%E5%AE%B3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BC%B8%E5%86%A4.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PlZV8vgXQMg/UC8fUjAh3RI/AAAAAAAALdU/-ujvx5ywIzU/s320/%E7%84%A6%E4%B8%9C%E6%B5%B7%E7%AC%AC1%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%9B%E5%86%9B%E5%90%8E%E4%BB%A3%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E5%B7%A5%E5%BC%A0%E8%8D%A3%E6%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%B7%E6%AD%A3%E7%A5%A5%E5%AE%B3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BC%B8%E5%86%A4.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>焦东海为农民工张荣才被院长康正祥害死伸冤</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HVjr4oHYRuw/UC8fc7prEsI/AAAAAAAALdc/yn3fpdnNeXo/s1600/201208181137china4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-HVjr4oHYRuw/UC8fc7prEsI/AAAAAAAALdc/yn3fpdnNeXo/s320/201208181137china4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>各地访民集会支持焦东海医生</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8218164801794217642?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[9503,19196]}